      "file": "src/flask/app.py",
      "expected": "from_envvar('APP_SETTINGS') should override the default None value set by from_object('default_settings'), so the production secret key from the env config file takes effect",
      "actual": "The default value (None or a dev key from default_settings) leaks through because a direct assignment app.config['SECRET_KEY'] = <default_value> placed after from_envvar() overwrites what from_envvar() loaded, restoring the default",
